            <title><![CDATA[Like a Dragon: Pirate Yakuza in Hawaii DLC costume ‘Dragon of Dojima’ available as free bonus to SEGA email subscribers]]></title>
            <link>https://www.gematsu.com/2024/11/like-a-dragon-pirate-yakuza-in-hawaii-dlc-costume-dragon-of-dojima-available-as-free-bonus-to-sega-email-subscribers</link>
