            <content:encoded><![CDATA[https://www.gematsu.com/2024/11/like-a-dragon-pirate-yakuza-in-hawaii-dlc-costume-dragon-of-dojima-available-as-free-bonus-to-sega-email-subscribers<br/><br/><div id="readability-page-1" class="page"><div>

    <ul>
    <li><a href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/pc">PC</a></li><li><a href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/playstation/ps4">PS4</a></li><li><a href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/playstation/ps5">PS5</a></li><li><a href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/xbox/xbox-one">Xbox One</a></li><li><a href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/xbox/xbox-series">Xbox Series</a></li>    </ul>

    
    <p><span>Subscribe before February 25, 2025 to get your download code.</span>
      </p></div><div><p>Users who <a href="https://www.sega.com/like-a-dragon-pirate-yakuza-in-hawaii-sign-up/" rel="noopener" target="_blank">subscribe to email updates</a> from <a title="Companies > SEGA [2,624 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/companies/sega">SEGA</a> by February 25, 2025 will receive a download code for Kazuma Kiryu’s “Dragon of Dojima” outfit for Majima Goro in <em><a title="Games > Like a Dragon: Pirate Yakuza in Hawaii [3 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/like-a-dragon-pirate-yakuza-in-hawaii">Like a Dragon: Pirate Yakuza in Hawaii</a></em>, publisher SEGA and developer <a title="Companies > Ryu Ga Gotoku Studio [475 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/companies/sega/ryu-ga-gotoku-studio">Ryu Ga Gotoku Studio</a> announced. <span id="more-926411"></span></p><figure><a data-featherlight="image" href="https://www.gematsu.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/LaD-Yakuza_11-07-24_Outfit.jpg"></a></figure><p><em>Like a Dragon: Pirate Yakuza in Hawaii</em> is due out for <a title="Platforms > PS5 [8,320 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/playstation/ps5">PlayStation 5</a>, <a title="Platforms > Xbox Series [6,355 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/xbox/xbox-series">Xbox Series</a>, <a title="Platforms > PS4 [27,415 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/playstation/ps4">PlayStation 4</a>, <a title="Platforms > Xbox One [13,616 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/xbox/xbox-one">Xbox One</a>, and <a title="Platforms > PC [21,645 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/pc">PC</a> via <a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/3061810/Like_a_Dragon_Pirate_Yakuza_in_Hawaii/" rel="noopener" target="_blank">Steam</a> and <a href="https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/store/p/like-a-dragon-pirate-yakuza-in-hawaii/9p1303fcxw6x" rel="noopener" target="_blank">Microsoft Store</a> on February 21, 2025 worldwide.</p><p>Watch a trailer showcasing the outfit below.</p><h2><span>Kazuma Kiryu Special Outfit Trailer</span></h2><p><iframe title="Like a Dragon: Pirate Yakuza in Hawaii | Kazuma Kiryu Special Outfit" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/uLnWRcF42u4?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></p><!-- AD: content -->
